<h3 class="date"><a href="/2007/oct/05/">&#x27a0;</a> October 5, 2007</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    <div class="flickrentry entry">
        <h4>Helpful Reminder</h4>

        <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/groovymother/1493855081/"><img class="flickrphoto" alt="Helpful Reminder" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2367/1493855081_58a406a474_m.jpg" height="180" width="240" /></a>

        <p>
            <p>You have twenty minutes to run, if you want to catch the T home.  Stupid 8:30pm starts!</p>
        </p>

